Subject: Re: all/6253: message-box
Date: Wed, 7 May 2003 11:10:53 -0500

 This code:
 
   (message-box "title" "message" #f '(yes-no))
 
 returns either 
 
   'yes
 
 or
 
   'no
 
 when clicking on the respective buttons.
 
 hth,
 Robby
